1) Contact Support

Get help now

Email us and well respond as soon as possible.

Email: support@phenohunt.com

Hours: MonFri, 9:0017:00 Pacific

Expected first response: within two business days.

Include details: device model, iOS version, app version (Settings About), and steps to reproduce.

Privacy requests

For data exports or deletion requests, use:

Email: privacy@phenohunt.com

We verify identity and respond per applicable law.

See also: Privacy Policy.

2) Quick FAQ

How do I reset my password?

On the signin screen, tap Forgot password? and follow the instructions sent to your email.

How do I delete my account?

In the app: Account Settings Delete Account. You can also email privacy@phenohunt.com.

My photos arent syncing.

Check connectivity and try again. If the issue persists, sign out and back in. Still stuck? Email us with your device and app version.

3) Troubleshooting

Basic steps

  • Ensure youre on the latest app version (TestFlight or App Store).
  • Forcequit and reopen the app.
  • Verify network connection (WiFi or Cellular).
  • Sign out and sign back in.

Collect logs for support

In the app, take screenshots of any error messages. Note the time and what you were doing. Attach to your email to support.

Device model iOS version App version Steps taken

5) About Phenohunt

Phenohunt is a recordkeeping and organization app by Soco Supply, LLC designed for lawful, educational tracking of plant phenotypes. It helps you document growth, compare phenos, and keep detailed notes and photos all synced across your devices.

Who it's for

Growers, breeders, and hobbyists who want a clean, structured way to document phenohunts.

Availability

iOS app via the App Store (link will appear here when available). Web access is coming soon.

6) Key Features

Structured records

Track phenohunts, phenos, ratings, and observations with photos and tags.

Crossdevice sync

Your data stays with you across devices. Designed for reliability, with offlinefriendly workflows.

Fast search

Find any pheno, photo, or record quickly with robust filters.

Export & portability

Export your data whenever you need it. Youre in control.
